     H            Y.
     F** UTLR76 ***********************************************************
     F*  UTILITY- GET LAST USE DATE OF OBJECT
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR76'
     F*                    PARM           $OBJ   10
     F*                    PARM           $LYMD   8
     F*                    PARM           $RTN    1
     F*   IN  $OBJ   10A   OBJECT
     F*   OUT $LYMD   8A   LAST USE DATE
     F*       $RTN    1A   RETURN (BLANK: OK, *: ERROR)
     F******************************************************************
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      *
